Class SimpleFutureAction<T>

  • Object
    • org.apache.spark.SimpleFutureAction<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class SimpleFutureAction<T>
extends Object
implements FutureAction<T>
    A FutureAction holding the result of an action that triggers a single job. Examples include count, collect, reduce.
